COMPILING
--------------------------------------------------------------

Either use the Makefile :

	make

Or you can compile the reciver.java and sender.java files individually by :
	
	javac sender.java
	javac receiver.java


RUNNING
--------------------------------------------------------------

Sender :
	
	java sender [-l <loss parameter>] <receiver_ip>

if loss parameter = 1, then each packet is dropped at the sender itself with probability 0.05
if loss parameter = 0, then each packet is dropped at the sender itself with probability 0


Receiver :

	java receiver
